title: Meet the 32 Women Vying for Matt James’ Heart
description:
The Season 25 cast of “The Bachelor” is revealed, and Rachel and Becca aren't holding back on their thoughts! Find out who the 32 women competing for Matt James’ heart are and what our hosts have to say about it. 

To see the headshots and get more info on the newly announced cast, visit BachelorNation.com

Don’t forget to rate and subscribe so you never miss an episode.
